description:
&lt;p&gt;The staffbank for Epsom and St Helier are looking for a Patient and Visitor guide to join the bank and work various hours across both site with full time hours possible!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The purpose of the Patient and Visitor guide is to ensure that patients feel welcomed and are supported to achieve infection control requirements on entering Trust premises following the COVID-19 pandemic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main elements of the role include welcoming patients, visitors and staff at Trust entrances and providing personal protective equipment and hand hygiene support where appropriate. Patients and visitors are also guided to use the correct hospital entrance / exit to support the use of COVID-19 secure pathways for patients attending for planned procedures and /or diagnostic treatments..&lt;/p&gt;
